 Q. At the players' meeting last night, it was decided that The Ryder Cup captain would be announced in two weeks' time; what are your thoughts about that?
 SERGIO GARCÃA: I think that there's a lot of possibilities for Ryder Cup Captaincy. I think it's fine. I don't think there's any hurry on it. It's not like The European Team is going to be done this week or anything like that. 
